race.comment: Going with the veteran EXTRAVAGENT LAD (3) who has won four times at 1000m. Led but found a couple better last start over 1100m here when second-up. Has raced five times third-up and is yet to miss the placings. In a tricky affair he appeals as a safe each-way option. BATTLE HYMN (2) returned from a seven-month spell and recorded his third win from just four starts when he toughed it out over 1100m at Hawkesbury four weeks ago. Beaten a nose at his only other 1000m run. Will race handy and give a great sight. WELCOME GYPSY (9) charged home to score over 900m at Newcastle last time. Will sit a bit closer with so many runners coming out and she is one to watch for late in the piece. The promising LYLES (8) returns from a spell. Beaten a whisker first-up last prep over 1200m at Rosehill. Trialling in great style and will be well found in betting with McDonald the pilot. MAILATA (6) is another with claims first-up from a six-month break.
